Text: lunch tomorrow Cc Charlespst CharlieWould it be possible to reschedule our lunch for sometime next week say Tuesday I guess the rest of the guys had planned a lunch on Friday with additional UT alumniEnron employees You are welcome to join us however I know you said you would prefer a smaller group I definitely want to visit with you about your experiences here at Enron Just let me know what works ThanksVance

RE LunchCharlespst No problem Thanks Original Message From Weldon V Charles Sent Thursday May PM To Schneider Eric Holtzman Vance Subject RE Lunch Lets shoot for lunch next Tuesday Would one of you please contact me that am to see how the day is going Its been pretty hectic lately but I think we will be able to do it Thanks Charlie Original Message From Schneider Eric Sent Thursday May AM To Weldon V Charles Holtzman Vance Subject Lunch Charlie I spoke with Vance Holtzman yesterday about the of us getting together for lunch However Friday does not work because we are meeting up with a large group of interns for lunch on Friday Is it possible that we meet for lunch next Tuesday June Please let me know if this fits your schedule Thanks Eric Schneider Enron Broadband Services

RE FW LunchCharlespst I may not be available today as I have previous plans but I will know for sure later today Vance Original Message From Schneider Eric Sent Friday June AM To Weldon V Charles Cc Holtzman Vance Subject Re FW Lunch Charlie Is lunch an option today perhaps we could go late after to miss the rush Eric Schneider Enron Broadband Services

RE lunchCharlespst My prior plans are still on You guys go ahead and I will try to schedule something next week with you Have a good weekend Vance Original Message From Schneider Eric Sent Friday June AM To Holtzman Vance Weldon V Charles Subject lunch If you guys havent gone to lunch yet its Im still game Eric Schneider Enron Broadband Services
